[BitcoinGet](http://www.bitcoinget.com) is an online rewards program that enables users to earn bitcoins for their web activity. To participate, users are not required to submit any information other than their Bitcoin address used to receive payments.

## Program

Users are able to earn bitcoins in a variety of ways:

* Tasks - Users have the opportunity complete a wide range simple tasks, such collecting data for various companies. This option is powered by CrowdFlower, a crowdsourcing company.

* Videos - Users can watch videos in a similar fashion to YouTube. To combat the use of bots, a CAPTCHA code must be entered after watching a video to receive credit.

* Special Offers - Users can complete offers, such as surveys, free trials, and sign-ups, from various companies. Additional information, such as a real email address, is often required by the offering companies.

